### ============================================================
### query-burst-msa order-service API
### Base URL: http://localhost:18115
### ============================================================

# @no-log

### Health
GET http://localhost:18115/actuator/health

### ============================================================
### [DATA INIT]
### ============================================================

### 테스트 데이터 적재 시작
POST http://localhost:18115/api/data-init

### 테스트 데이터 적재 상태 확인
GET http://localhost:18115/api/data-init/status

### ============================================================
### [ORDER]
### ============================================================

### 주문 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:18115/api/orders?size=20

### 주문 목록 조회 - 다음 페이지
GET http://localhost:18115/api/orders?cursor=1000&size=20

### 주문 상세 조회
GET http://localhost:18115/api/orders/1

### 주문 생성
POST http://localhost:18115/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: order-demo-1

{
  "memberId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 120000
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 350000
    }
  ]
}

### 결제 처리
PATCH http://localhost:18115/api/orders/1/pay

### 배송 시작
PATCH http://localhost:18115/api/orders/1/ship

### 배송 완료
PATCH http://localhost:18115/api/orders/1/deliver

### 주문 취소
DELETE http://localhost:18115/api/orders/1
